\r\n\t<p class="quote">*<em> There\xe2\x80\x99s Sunshine in My Soul Today,</em> lyrics by Eliza E. Hewitt<br />\r\n\t\t**<em> It Is No Secret What God Can Do,</em> lyrics by Stuart Hamblen</p>\r\n\t\r\n\t<hr /><br /><h2 style="text-align: center;" align="center">THE TRUE CHURCH</h2>\r\n\t<table align="center" border="0" cellpadding="3" cellspacing="0" width="650"><tbody>\r\n\t\t<tr><td valign="top" width="95">FALSE</td>\r\n\t\t\t<td valign="top" width="545">God\xe2\x80\x99s true church is an organization.</td></tr>\r\n\t\t<tr><td valign="top">TRUE</td><td valign="top">God\'s true church is composed of His people.<sup id="footnote-tooltip-note-a" class="footnote-tooltip-text" onclick="footnote_moveToAnchor(\'footnote-reference-note-a\')" >a</sup><span class="footnote-tooltip" id="footnote-tooltip-text-note-a" style=" display: none;"><span class="fn-container"><span class="fn-ref">Manuscript Releases, Vol. 17, pp. 81-82</span><span class="fn-body">\r\n\t\t\tGod has a church. It is not the great cathedral, neither is it the national establishment, neither is it the various denominations; it is the people who love God and keep His commandments. \xe2\x80\xa6 Where Christ is, even among the humble few, this is Christ\'s church, for the presence of the High and Holy One who inhabiteth eternity can alone constitute a church.</span></span><span class="fn-container">\r\n\t\t\t<span class="fn-ref">Acts of the Apostles, pp. 11-12</span><span class="fn-body">\r\n\t\t\tFrom the beginning, faithful souls have constituted the church on earth. \xe2\x80\xa6 Through centuries of persecution, conflict, and darkness, God has sustained His church. Not one cloud has fallen upon it that He has not prepared for; not one opposing force has risen to counterwork His work, that He has not foreseen\xe2\x80\xa6 He has not left His church forsaken, but has traced in prophetic declarations what would occur\xe2\x80\xa6 </span></span></span><script type="text/javascript">  jQuery("#footnote-tooltip-note-a").tooltip({ tip: "#footnote-tooltip-text-note-a", tipClass: "footnote-tooltip", effect: "fade", fadeOutSpeed: 100, predelay: 400, position: "bottom center", relative: true, offset: [0, 10]}).dynamic({bottom: {direction: "down", bounce: true}}); </script><br /><br /></td></tr>\r\n\t\t<tr><td valign="top">FALSE</td>\r\n\t\t\t<td valign="top">God\xe2\x80\x99s church is pure and holy.</td></tr>\r\n\t\t<tr><td valign="top">TRUE</td><td valign="top">God\xe2\x80\x99s church is called Laodicea, because she is blind to her own problems. There are tares in God\xe2\x80\x99s church, but it is about to be purified.<sup id="footnote-tooltip-note-b" class="footnote-tooltip-text" onclick="footnote_moveToAnchor(\'footnote-reference-note-b\')" >b</sup><span class="footnote-tooltip" id="footnote-tooltip-text-note-b" style=" display: none;"><span class="fn-container"><span class="fn-body">In \xe2\x80\x9c<a title="22. The SDA Church" href="http://www.formypeople.org/dream/22-the-sda-church/" target="_blank">The SDA Church</a>\xe2\x80\x9d dream, the church building represents the SDA organization. The first part of the dream, before the \xe2\x80\x9ctares\xe2\x80\x9d left the building, represents the church militant (both wheat and tares). The part of the dream where the tares have left and the building is still intact represents the church triumphant (only the wheat). As in the \xe2\x80\x9c<a title="36. Two Cars" href="http://www.formypeople.org/dream/36-two-cars/" target="_blank">Two Cars</a>\xe2\x80\x9d dream, the tares go to the left and the wheat go to the right.<br /><br /> \r\n\t\t\t\xe2\x80\x9c<a title="42. The Vessel" href="http://www.formypeople.org/dream/42-the-vessel/" target="_blank">The Vessel</a>\xe2\x80\x9d dream symbolizes the SDA organization at this time and how it is about to go to the right, to be purified. We believe as Ellen White stated that the Sunday law, among other things, will help to purify the church.<br /><br /> \r\n\t\t\tThe \xe2\x80\x9c<a title="64. Final Events and the First Supper" href="http://www.formypeople.org/dream/64-final-events-and-the-first-supper/" target="_blank">Final Events</a>\xe2\x80\x9d dream shows that fire is part of what God will use to purify His church.</span></span></span><script type="text/javascript">  jQuery("#footnote-tooltip-note-b").tooltip({ tip: "#footnote-tooltip-text-note-b", tipClass: "footnote-tooltip", effect: "fade", fadeOutSpeed: 100, predelay: 400, position: "bottom center", relative: true, offset: [0, 10]}).dynamic({bottom: {direction: "down", bounce: true}}); </script><br /><br /></td></tr>\r\n\t\t<tr><td valign="top">FALSE</td><td valign="top">The For My People Ministry says that the SDA organization is Babylon.</td></tr>\r\n\t\t<tr><td valign="top">TRUE</td><td valign="top">The For My People Ministry says that the SDA organization is backsliding and in the omega of apostasy.<sup id="footnote-tooltip-note-c" class="footnote-tooltip-text" onclick="footnote_moveToAnchor(\'footnote-reference-note-c\')" >c</sup><span class="footnote-tooltip" id="footnote-tooltip-text-note-c" style=" display: none;"><span class="fn-container"><span class="fn-ref">Selected Messages, Book 2, p. 68</span><span class="fn-body">\r\n\t\t\tThe wine of Babylon is the exalting of the false and spurious Sabbath above the Sabbath which the Lord Jehovah hath blessed and sanctified for the use of man, also [it is] the immortality of the soul. These kindred heresies, and the rejection of the truth, convert the church into Babylon.</span></span></span><script type="text/javascript">  jQuery("#footnote-tooltip-note-c").tooltip({ tip: "#footnote-tooltip-text-note-c", tipClass: "footnote-tooltip", effect: "fade", fadeOutSpeed: 100, predelay: 400, position: "bottom center", relative: true, offset: [0, 10]}).dynamic({bottom: {direction: "down", bounce: true}}); </script><br /><br /></td></tr>\r\n\t\t<tr><td valign="top">FALSE</td><td valign="top">All the leaders of the SDA organization are true and faithful to God.</td></tr>\r\n\t\t<tr><td valign="top">TRUE</td><td valign="top">Many enemies of God have infiltrated the SDA organization, and they have led and are leading it away from the \xe2\x80\x9cold paths.\xe2\x80\x9d<sup id="footnote-tooltip-note-d" class="footnote-tooltip-text" onclick="footnote_moveToAnchor(\'footnote-reference-note-d\')" >d</sup><span class="footnote-tooltip" id="footnote-tooltip-text-note-d" style=" display: none;"><span class="fn-container"><span class="fn-body">Notice the following quotes from the dream, \xe2\x80\x9c<a title="58. The Senior Pastor" href="http://www.formypeople.org/dream/58-the-senior-pastor/" target="_blank">The Senior Pastor</a>\xe2\x80\x9d<br /><br />\r\n\t\t\tLet those who study and follow the blueprint sent to God\xe2\x80\x99s baker, Ellen White, simply call themselves \xe2\x80\x9cThe Church.\xe2\x80\x9d Just as God instructed Moses to tell the Israelites, \xe2\x80\x9cI AM hath sent me unto you,\xe2\x80\x9d let His people know that \xe2\x80\x9cThe Church\xe2\x80\x9d is His church and that His church will not fall, but will continue.<br /><br />\r\n\t\t\tThe unfaithful in the Seventh-day Adventist organization are the offshoots. However, the organization is not Babylon, but it has fallen into deep apostasy. God\xe2\x80\x99s true church is the church that holds to the blueprint handed down from the Great I AM. Even if it is called an offshoot, know that those who have the true recipe for baking bread in their hands are God\xe2\x80\x99s true church. His church is His people who bake bread according to His directions. It is not the organization that is secretly led by the Catholic Church. It is not the organization that is controlled by spies and Jesuits placed to control the worship services according to the directions of the Catholic Church. Many can clearly see that this is not what the heavenly Father has directed. He has His people, His Church.</span></span></span><script type="text/javascript">  jQuery("#footnote-tooltip-note-d").tooltip({ tip: "#footnote-tooltip-text-note-d", tipClass: "footnote-tooltip", effect: "fade", fadeOutSpeed: 100, predelay: 400, position: "bottom center", relative: true, offset: [0, 10]}).dynamic({bottom: {direction: "down", bounce: true}}); </script><br /><br /></td></tr>\r\n\t\t<tr><td valign="top">FALSE</td><td valign="top">The For My People Ministry is a sect that tries to draw people away from the SDA organization.</td></tr>\r\n\t\t<tr><td valign="top">TRUE</td><td valign="top">The For My People Ministry emphasizes the importance of maintaining membership in the SDA organization, because it is God\xe2\x80\x99s last-day church, even if it is in apostasy.<sup id="footnote-tooltip-note-e" class="footnote-tooltip-text" onclick="footnote_moveToAnchor(\'footnote-reference-note-e\')" >e</sup><span class="footnote-tooltip" id="footnote-tooltip-text-note-e" style=" display: none;"><span class="fn-container"><span class="fn-body">Of course, if faithful members are disfellowshipped, that does not mean they are no longer Adventists. What is important is that their names are on the books of heaven.</span></span></span><script type="text/javascript">  jQuery("#footnote-tooltip-note-e").tooltip({ tip: "#footnote-tooltip-text-note-e", tipClass: "footnote-tooltip", effect: "fade", fadeOutSpeed: 100, predelay: 400, position: "bottom center", relative: true, offset: [0, 10]}).dynamic({bottom: {direction: "down", bounce: true}}); </script><br /><br /></td></tr>\r\n\t\t<tr><td valign="top">FALSE</td><td valign="top">God\xe2\x80\x99s people are to continue to faithfully attend and support their local SDA churches.</td></tr>\r\n\t\t<tr><td valign="top">TRUE</td><td valign="top">It is imperative that God\xe2\x80\x99s people not attend SDA churches where the Holy Spirit is not present. It may be necessary to have home church.<sup id="footnote-tooltip-note-f" class="footnote-tooltip-text" onclick="footnote_moveToAnchor(\'footnote-reference-note-f\')" >f</sup><span class="footnote-tooltip" id="footnote-tooltip-text-note-f" style=" display: none;"><span class="fn-container"><span class="fn-ref">Matthew 18:20</span><span class="fn-body">\r\n\t\t\tFor where two or three are gathered together in my name, there am I in the midst of them.</span></span>\r\n\t\t\t<span class="fn-container"><span class="fn-ref">Life Sketches of Ellen G. White, p. 259</span><span class="fn-body">\r\n\t\t\tI would encourage those who assemble in little companies to worship God. Brethren and sisters, be not disheartened because you are so few in number.</span></span>\r\n\t\t\t<span class="fn-container"><span class="fn-ref">Early Writings, pp. 124-125 </span><span class="fn-body">\r\n\t\t\tI was shown the necessity of those who believe that we are having the last message of mercy, being separate from those who are daily imbibing new errors. I saw that neither young nor old should attend their meetings; for it is wrong to thus encourage them while they teach error that is a deadly poison to the soul and teach for doctrines the commandments of men. The influence of such gatherings is not good. \xe2\x80\xa6 God is displeased with us when we go to listen to error, without being obliged to go; for unless He sends us to those meetings where error is forced home to the people by the power of the will, He will not keep us. The angels cease their watchful care over us, and we are left to the buffetings of the enemy, to be darkened and weakened by him and the power of his evil angels; and the light around us becomes contaminated with the darkness.</span></span>\r\n\t\t\t<span class="fn-container"><span class="fn-ref">The Review and Herald, October 14, 1884</span><span class="fn-body">\r\n\t\t\tOn the Sabbath the few friends here assembled in Edson\'s parlor for a Sabbath-school. There are four families--twelve persons in all--who usually meet for worship. Edson conducts the Sabbath-school when he is at home. After Sabbath-school they either have a Bible-reading or a prayer and social meeting. This is as it should be. The family altar should be established in every home; and if in any locality there are no more than two or three of like precious faith, they should meet together.</span></span></span><script type="text/javascript">  jQuery("#footnote-tooltip-note-f").tooltip({ tip: "#footnote-tooltip-text-note-f", tipClass: "footnote-tooltip", effect: "fade", fadeOutSpeed: 100, predelay: 400, position: "bottom center", relative: true, offset: [0, 10]}).dynamic({bottom: {direction: "down", bounce: true}}); </script><br /><br /></td></tr>\r\n\t\t<tr><td valign="top">FALSE</td><td valign="top">We must unite with our local SDA conference and support it even though it teaches error.</td></tr>\r\n\t\t<tr><td valign="top">TRUE</td><td valign="top">Truth brings division and separation.<sup id="footnote-tooltip-note-g" class="footnote-tooltip-text" onclick="footnote_moveToAnchor(\'footnote-reference-note-g\')" >g</sup><span class="footnote-tooltip" id="footnote-tooltip-text-note-g" style=" display: none;"><span class="fn-container"><span class="fn-ref">John 7:43</span><span class="fn-body">\r\n\t\t\tSo there was a division among the people because of him [Jesus]. </span></span>\r\n\t\t\t<span class="fn-container"><span class="fn-ref">Luke 12:51</span><span class="fn-body">\r\n\t\t\tSuppose ye that I am come to give peace on earth? I tell you, Nay; but rather division... </span></span>\r\n\t\t\t<span class="fn-container"><span class="fn-ref">The Great Controversy, p. 45</span><span class="fn-body">\r\n\t\t\tIf unity could be secured only by the compromise of truth and righteousness, then let there be difference, and even war.</span></span></span><script type="text/javascript">  jQuery("#footnote-tooltip-note-g").tooltip({ tip: "#footnote-tooltip-text-note-g", tipClass: "footnote-tooltip", effect: "fade", fadeOutSpeed: 100, predelay: 400, position: "bottom center", relative: true, offset: [0, 10]}).dynamic({bottom: {direction: "down", bounce: true}}); </script><br /><br /></td></tr>\r\n\t\t<tr><td valign="top">FALSE</td><td valign="top">God will separate the wheat from the tares, without any human participation.</td></tr>\r\n\t\t<tr><td valign="top">TRUE</td><td valign="top">God says that His people must cooperate with Him by separating themselves from sin and sinners. The Holy Spirit will convict and guide His people on how to do this.<sup id="footnote-tooltip-note-h" class="footnote-tooltip-text" onclick="footnote_moveToAnchor(\'footnote-reference-note-h\')" >h</sup><span class="footnote-tooltip" id="footnote-tooltip-text-note-h" style=" display: none;"><span class="fn-container"><span class="fn-ref">The Signs of the Times, January 13, 1881</span><span class="fn-body">\r\n\t\t\tGod requires his people to separate themselves from sin and sinners, choosing their society only when there is an opportunity to do them good. We cannot be too decided in shunning the company of all who have in any way exerted an influence to draw us into sin. None will be punished with greater severity than those who have enticed God\'s people from their integrity.</span></span></span><script type="text/javascript">  jQuery("#footnote-tooltip-note-h").tooltip({ tip: "#footnote-tooltip-text-note-h", tipClass: "footnote-tooltip", effect: "fade", fadeOutSpeed: 100, predelay: 400, position: "bottom center", relative: true, offset: [0, 10]}).dynamic({bottom: {direction: "down", bounce: true}}); </script></td></tr></tbody></table>\r\n\t<br />\r\n\t<hr>\r\n\t<br />\r\n<div class="footnote-reference-container-alpha"><table class="footnote-reference-table-alpha"><tbody><tr><td class="footnote-index"><span id="footnote-reference-note-a">a.</span></td><td class="footnote-link"><span onclick="footnote_moveToAnchor(\'footnote-tooltip-note-a\')"> &uarr; </span></td><td class="footnote-text"><span class="fn-container"><span class="fn-ref">Manuscript Releases, Vol. 17, pp. 81-82</span><span class="fn-body">\r\n\t\t\tGod has a church. It is not the great cathedral, neither is it the national establishment, neither is it the various denominations; it is the people who love God and keep His commandments. \xe2\x80\xa6 Where Christ is, even among the humble few, this is Christ\'s church, for the presence of the High and Holy One who inhabiteth eternity can alone constitute a church.</span></span><span class="fn-container">\r\n\t\t\t<span class="fn-ref">Acts of the Apostles, pp. 11-12</span><span class="fn-body">\r\n\t\t\tFrom the beginning, faithful souls have constituted the church on earth. \xe2\x80\xa6 Through centuries of persecution, conflict, and darkness, God has sustained His church. Not one cloud has fallen upon it that He has not prepared for; not one opposing force has risen to counterwork His work, that He has not foreseen\xe2\x80\xa6 He has not left His church forsaken, but has traced in prophetic declarations what would occur\xe2\x80\xa6 </span></span></td></tr><tr><td class="footnote-index"><span id="footnote-reference-note-b">b.</span></td><td class="footnote-link"><span onclick="footnote_moveToAnchor(\'footnote-tooltip-note-b\')"> &uarr; </span></td><td class="footnote-text"><span class="fn-container"><span class="fn-body">In \xe2\x80\x9c<a title="22. The SDA Church" href="http://www.formypeople.org/dream/22-the-sda-church/" target="_blank">The SDA Church</a>\xe2\x80\x9d dream, the church building represents the SDA organization. The first part of the dream, before the \xe2\x80\x9ctares\xe2\x80\x9d left the building, represents the church militant (both wheat and tares). The part of the dream where the tares have left and the building is still intact represents the church triumphant (only the wheat). As in the \xe2\x80\x9c<a title="36. Two Cars" href="http://www.formypeople.org/dream/36-two-cars/" target="_blank">Two Cars</a>\xe2\x80\x9d dream, the tares go to the left and the wheat go to the right.<br /><br /> \r\n\t\t\t\xe2\x80\x9c<a title="42. The Vessel" href="http://www.formypeople.org/dream/42-the-vessel/" target="_blank">The Vessel</a>\xe2\x80\x9d dream symbolizes the SDA organization at this time and how it is about to go to the right, to be purified. We believe as Ellen White stated that the Sunday law, among other things, will help to purify the church.<br /><br /> \r\n\t\t\tThe \xe2\x80\x9c<a title="64. Final Events and the First Supper" href="http://www.formypeople.org/dream/64-final-events-and-the-first-supper/" target="_blank">Final Events</a>\xe2\x80\x9d dream shows that fire is part of what God will use to purify His church.</span></span></td></tr><tr><td class="footnote-index"><span id="footnote-reference-note-c">c.</span></td><td class="footnote-link"><span onclick="footnote_moveToAnchor(\'footnote-tooltip-note-c\')"> &uarr; </span></td><td class="footnote-text"><span class="fn-container"><span class="fn-ref">Selected Messages, Book 2, p. 68</span><span class="fn-body">\r\n\t\t\tThe wine of Babylon is the exalting of the false and spurious Sabbath above the Sabbath which the Lord Jehovah hath blessed and sanctified for the use of man, also [it is] the immortality of the soul. These kindred heresies, and the rejection of the truth, convert the church into Babylon.</span></span></td></tr><tr><td class="footnote-index"><span id="footnote-reference-note-d">d.</span></td><td class="footnote-link"><span onclick="footnote_moveToAnchor(\'footnote-tooltip-note-d\')"> &uarr; </span></td><td class="footnote-text"><span class="fn-container"><span class="fn-body">Notice the following quotes from the dream, \xe2\x80\x9c<a title="58. The Senior Pastor" href="http://www.formypeople.org/dream/58-the-senior-pastor/" target="_blank">The Senior Pastor</a>\xe2\x80\x9d<br /><br />\r\n\t\t\tLet those who study and follow the blueprint sent to God\xe2\x80\x99s baker, Ellen White, simply call themselves \xe2\x80\x9cThe Church.\xe2\x80\x9d Just as God instructed Moses to tell the Israelites, \xe2\x80\x9cI AM hath sent me unto you,\xe2\x80\x9d let His people know that \xe2\x80\x9cThe Church\xe2\x80\x9d is His church and that His church will not fall, but will continue.<br /><br />\r\n\t\t\tThe unfaithful in the Seventh-day Adventist organization are the offshoots. However, the organization is not Babylon, but it has fallen into deep apostasy. God\xe2\x80\x99s true church is the church that holds to the blueprint handed down from the Great I AM. Even if it is called an offshoot, know that those who have the true recipe for baking bread in their hands are God\xe2\x80\x99s true church. His church is His people who bake bread according to His directions. It is not the organization that is secretly led by the Catholic Church. It is not the organization that is controlled by spies and Jesuits placed to control the worship services according to the directions of the Catholic Church. Many can clearly see that this is not what the heavenly Father has directed. He has His people, His Church.</span></span></td></tr><tr><td class="footnote-index"><span id="footnote-reference-note-e">e.</span></td><td class="footnote-link"><span onclick="footnote_moveToAnchor(\'footnote-tooltip-note-e\')"> &uarr; </span></td><td class="footnote-text"><span class="fn-container"><span class="fn-body">Of course, if faithful members are disfellowshipped, that does not mean they are no longer Adventists. What is important is that their names are on the books of heaven.</span></span></td></tr><tr><td class="footnote-index"><span id="footnote-reference-note-f">f.</span></td><td class="footnote-link"><span onclick="footnote_moveToAnchor(\'footnote-tooltip-note-f\')"> &uarr; </span></td><td class="footnote-text"><span class="fn-container"><span class="fn-ref">Matthew 18:20</span><span class="fn-body">\r\n\t\t\tFor where two or three are gathered together in my name, there am I in the midst of them.</span></span>\r\n\t\t\t<span class="fn-container"><span class="fn-ref">Life Sketches of Ellen G. White, p. 259</span><span class="fn-body">\r\n\t\t\tI would encourage those who assemble in little companies to worship God. Brethren and sisters, be not disheartened because you are so few in number.</span></span>\r\n\t\t\t<span class="fn-container"><span class="fn-ref">Early Writings, pp. 124-125 </span><span class="fn-body">\r\n\t\t\tI was shown the necessity of those who believe that we are having the last message of mercy, being separate from those who are daily imbibing new errors. I saw that neither young nor old should attend their meetings; for it is wrong to thus encourage them while they teach error that is a deadly poison to the soul and teach for doctrines the commandments of men. The influence of such gatherings is not good. \xe2\x80\xa6 God is displeased with us when we go to listen to error, without being obliged to go; for unless He sends us to those meetings where error is forced home to the people by the power of the will, He will not keep us. The angels cease their watchful care over us, and we are left to the buffetings of the enemy, to be darkened and weakened by him and the power of his evil angels; and the light around us becomes contaminated with the darkness.</span></span>\r\n\t\t\t<span class="fn-container"><span class="fn-ref">The Review and Herald, October 14, 1884</span><span class="fn-body">\r\n\t\t\tOn the Sabbath the few friends here assembled in Edson\'s parlor for a Sabbath-school. There are four families--twelve persons in all--who usually meet for worship. Edson conducts the Sabbath-school when he is at home. After Sabbath-school they either have a Bible-reading or a prayer and social meeting. This is as it should be. The family altar should be established in every home; and if in any locality there are no more than two or three of like precious faith, they should meet together.</span></span></td></tr><tr><td class="footnote-index"><span id="footnote-reference-note-g">g.</span></td><td class="footnote-link"><span onclick="footnote_moveToAnchor(\'footnote-tooltip-note-g\')"> &uarr; </span></td><td class="footnote-text"><span class="fn-container"><span class="fn-ref">John 7:43</span><span class="fn-body">\r\n\t\t\tSo there was a division among the people because of him [Jesus]. </span></span>\r\n\t\t\t<span class="fn-container"><span class="fn-ref">Luke 12:51</span><span class="fn-body">\r\n\t\t\tSuppose ye that I am come to give peace on earth? I tell you, Nay; but rather division... </span></span>\r\n\t\t\t<span class="fn-container"><span class="fn-ref">The Great Controversy, p. 45</span><span class="fn-body">\r\n\t\t\tIf unity could be secured only by the compromise of truth and righteousness, then let there be difference, and even war.</span></span></td></tr><tr><td class="footnote-index"><span id="footnote-reference-note-h">h.</span></td><td class="footnote-link"><span onclick="footnote_moveToAnchor(\'footnote-tooltip-note-h\')"> &uarr; </span></td><td class="footnote-text"><span class="fn-container"><span class="fn-ref">The Signs of the Times, January 13, 1881</span><span class="fn-body">\r\n\t\t\tGod requires his people to separate themselves from sin and sinners, choosing their society only when there is an opportunity to do them good. We cannot be too decided in shunning the company of all who have in any way exerted an influence to draw us into sin. None will be punished with greater severity than those who have enticed God\'s people from their integrity.</span></span></td></tr></tbody></table></div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<!-- END OF Excerpt_end --></div><footer class="entry-footer">\n   <div class="nav-link-box">\n\n       <div class="share-box bottom"><div class="ssba"><div class="right"><div class="img-wrap download"><a href="http://www.formypeople.org/wp-content/uploads/pdf/dreams/en/en_69_god_Is_angry.pdf" title="PDF"><span class="fa-stack ">\n                            <i class="fa fa-circle fa-stack-2x"></i>\n                            <i class="fa fa-download fa-stack-1x fa-inverse"></i>\n                        </span></a></div><div class="img-wrap pri